{"tid":609819,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"美國哈迪斯想推出Spielbergers 史匹堡回應：不了","createTime":"2018-03-29T10:55:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T10:55:59.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"69b9b9ea199f748fa73976576221f1f2c6f81826","tid":609819,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T10:55:59.000Z","msg":"史蒂芬史匹柏(Steven Spielberg)或許是卡樂星漢堡(Carl`s Jr.)的紛絲，但他可不想自己的名字被用在上面。<br />\n<br />\n速食大公司週一(26日)透過推特宣布計劃將旗下一款炭烤滑堡(Charbroiled Sliders)重新命名為史匹柏堡(Spielbergers)來致敬大導以及3月29日即將於全美上映，虛擬實境主題的電影【一級玩家】。<br />\n<br />\n連鎖速食店推發消息，最後補充說：「@StevenSpielberg還沒簽署同意，但我們非常肯定他會願意的。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/CarlsJr/status/978253988142358530\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCarlsJr%2Fstatus%2F978253988142358530&d=p%2BAmfsbQCNPRbJRJW9%2F6llzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=b0340c87\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCarlsJr%2Fstatus%2F978253988142358530&h=3c4bcbd5\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/CarlsJr/status/978253988142358530</a><br />\n<br />\n恩，遺憾的是，事實並非如此。史匹柏拍了一部短片貼在自家製作公司安培林娛樂(Amblin Entertainment)推特上，對該行銷點子做出正式回應。<br />\n<br />\n史匹柏說：「嘿，大家好。最近卡樂星漢堡想把炭烤滑堡重新命名為史匹柏堡引發了我的注意。他們產品很棒，可是我打算跳過。發出停終要求。你無法這樣做。大夥抱歉囉。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/AmblinEnt/status/978732170788286464\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAmblinEnt%2Fstatus%2F978732170788286464&d=p%2BAmfsbQCNPRbJRJW9%2F6llzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=732c2a04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAmblinEnt%2Fstatus%2F978732170788286464&h=ad2c00f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/AmblinEnt/status/978732170788286464</a><br />\n<br />\n如此發展下，卡樂星漢堡抱有樂觀看法，選擇注意在大導說漢堡嘗起來&quot;很棒&quot;。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/CarlsJr/status/978734480029466625\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCarlsJr%2Fstatus%2F978734480029466625&d=p%2BAmfsbQCNPRbJRJW9%2F6llzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=ab34cbd9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCarlsJr%2Fstatus%2F978734480029466625&h=997a83ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/CarlsJr/status/978734480029466625</a><br />\n<br />\n漢堡並沒有跟【一級玩家】簽訂任何宣傳合作關係。不管究竟如何，華納影業表明不允許&quot;史匹柏堡&quot;的使用。華納影業於推特上寫下：「感謝對【一級玩家】 的熱愛，但這樣不准。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/wbpictures/status/978388089549697025\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fwbpictures%2Fstatus%2F978388089549697025&d=p%2BAmfsbQCNPRbJRJW9%2F6llzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=a556ef56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fwbpictures%2Fstatus%2F978388089549697025&h=668a8637\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/wbpictures/status/978388089549697025</a><br />\n<br />\n史匹柏回應前，卡樂星漢堡立刻瞄準導演貼出多則推文和影片。甚至驅車前往製片公司安培林娛樂和突襲【一級玩家】首映試圖給傳奇導演看看他們的漢堡。<br />\n當然，整齣戲有可能是華納影業與卡樂星漢堡計劃好的宣傳噱頭。無論如何，看起來&quot;史匹柏堡&quot;計劃目前已終止。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://changemovie.blogspot.hk/2018/03/carls-jr.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchangemovie.blogspot.hk%2F2018%2F03%2Fcarls-jr.html&d=p%2BAmfsbQCNPRbJRJW9%2F6llzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=58b43c33\" target=\"_blank\">http://changemovie.blogspot.hk/2018/03/carls-jr.html</a>"}]}